# Normalize line endings on commit; check out as LF on every platform.
# Overrides core.autocrlf so Windows clones do not silently re-introduce CRLF.
# Critical for a shell-only project: bash scripts with CRLF break on Linux/macOS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types so git never tries to normalize them.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
